spec_data.Name: texlive-tikzmark
spec_data.Description:
The tikzmark package defines a command to "remember" a position
on a page for later (or earlier) use, primarily (but not
exclusively) with TikZ.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:59:47 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Use TikZ's method of remembering a position on a page
